quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  41,1,"Haa, Miim"
  41,2,"A revelation from God, the Merciful Benefactor, the Merciful Redeemer"
  41,3,"A book of verses explained in detail. A Quran in Arabic, for people who know"
  41,4,"Giving good news and advice. Yet most of them turn away, so they do not hear"
  41,5,"They say, “Our hearts are under veils, concealed from that which you invite us, and in our ears is deafness, and between us and you is a screen. So do what you will, and for us, we will do what we will.”"
  41,6,"Say, “I am only a human being like you. It is revealed to me by inspiration that your God is one God. So stand true to Him, and ask for His forgiveness.” And woe to those who join gods with God"
  41,7,"Those who do not give zakat, and who deny the hereafter"
  41,8,For those who believe and do deeds of righteousness is a reward that will never fail